---
import { Picture } from "astro:assets";
import img from "~/assets/Liang.png";
import { SiteDescription, SiteTitle } from "~/config";
import MarkdownLayout from "~/layouts/MarkdownLayout.astro";
---

<MarkdownLayout
	title={SiteTitle}
	description={SiteDescription}
	hide={["title", "comments"]}
	currentNav="Home"
>
	<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 xl:flex-row">
		<Picture
			class="lg:max-w-xl"
			src={img}
			formats={["avif", "webp"]}
			alt="Taolinyinjiu favorite anime heroine "
			loading="eager"
		/>
		<div>
			<h1>Hello, 欢迎来到桃林饮酒的博客😋</h1>
			<p>
				这是一个由<a href="https://astro.build">Astro</a
				>框架部署的博客，在<a href="https://github.com/ladit">Ladit</a
				>的博客主题<a href="https://github.com/ladit/astro-blog-zozo"
					>astro-blog-zozo</a
				>的基础上进行二创，在这里一并致谢，同时感谢<a
					href="https://blog.zhilu.cyou/">纸鹿</a
				>帮我搭建的<a href="https://www.taolin.site/friends">友链</a
				>页面，嘻嘻（走来走去
			</p>
			<p>以下是这个博客站点所包含主要内容（或者说我的主要学习方向🤔）</p>
			<ul class="list-disc">
				<li>嵌入式微控制器开发 (以STM32F4, STM32H7, STC89C52为主)</li>
				<li>Proteus仿真设计 (以仿真STM32F103x, AT89C51/52为主)</li>
				<li>Multsim仿真设计 (以数字逻辑电路，数字信号处理为主)</li>
				<li>OpenCV (Open Computer Vision Library) 学习与实践</li>
				<li>A lot of Markdown and a bit of LaTeX</li>
				<li>ROS (Robot Operate System) based on Ubuntu 18.04</li>
				<li>ROS2 (Robot Operate System 2) based on Ubuntu 22.04</li>
				<li>PX4 Learning</li>
				<li>SolidWorks 3D建模 and 3D print</li>
				<li>Learning the Hw Ascend framework</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
</MarkdownLayout>
